name: universal unity
description: This artwork was created as part of the #Legato100 project, as cover art for "Nifty Sax Collection: Genesis #73 - Universal Unity". Legato100 is a collaborative project of 100 artworks for 100 music tracks. More: https://niftysax.com/legato100 It's a generative digital artwork, a collaboration between human and machine. It's meant to reflect a true reality that is messy, weird, colorful, and chaotic, and sometimes goes in unexpected directions but also where everything is interconnected in ways both seen and unseen.
